4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners. Over a duration of 16 weeks, students engage in three live online classes each week, with a maximum of 16 participants per class. The program covers essential skills in Windows, Linux, network and server administration, cloud security, and penetration testing. Moreover, it includes cyber threat intelligence analysis and risk management using data loss prevention strategies. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. The course is available in English and Spanish, with no prior experience required. For more details, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop